{"title":"php的if和java的if比较","date":"2018-05-21T02:45:00.000Z","link":"post/108","categories":["Other"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:28:10.553Z","content":"<p>php中的<code>if</code>语句是<strong>弱类型</strong>，即<code>if（）</code>中的判断语句不必是<strong>boolean类型</strong>的。<br><a id=\"more\"></a><br>例：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;?php</span><br><span class=\"line\">if(0)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\techo &apos;true&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\techo &apos;false&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">输出： false; //0代表着false</span><br><span class=\"line\">?&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>而java中的<code>if()</code>的条件必须是<strong>boolean类型</strong>的。<br>即<code>if(0)</code>这样写是不可以的，会报错。要写成如下的格式：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">if(1&lt;2)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tsystem.out.printf(&quot;true&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tsystem.out.printf(&quot;flase&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">输出：true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"php Incorrect Table Name错误","link":"post/112"},"next":{"title":"oracle中 =: 和 :=","link":"post/74"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/108/"}